---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Our Story" description="The story behind Paul's Homemade Ice Cream — from a gifted ice cream machine to South Africa's favourite handcrafted scoops.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-pauls-dark-blue text-white py-20 md:py-28 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">The man. The scoop. The story.</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70">How a gifted ice cream machine started it all</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24 space-y-16">
    <!-- Origin -->
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Where It All Began</h2>
      <p class="text-pauls-dark-blue/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        It started with an ice cream machine — a gift that sparked something extraordinary. Paul began churning small batches of bold, handcrafted ice cream and taking them to local Johannesburg markets. The response was immediate and enthusiastic.
      </p>
      <p class="text-pauls-dark-blue/70 leading-relaxed">
        In 2014, Paul partnered with his friend Josh to fill a gap they both saw — the lack of premium, creative ice cream in South Africa. Together they set out to make high-quality, playful desserts accessible to everyone.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Growth -->
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">From Scoops to a Movement</h2>
      <p class="text-pauls-dark-blue/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        What started as scoops quickly expanded into sticks, sandwiches, cakes, and even pet treats. Paul's Homemade grew to over 30 stores nationwide — but the heart of the brand remained the same: handcrafted quality and a sense of fun in every bite.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission -->
    <div class="bg-pauls-light-blue/40 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
      <blockquote class="text-lg md:text-xl italic text-pauls-dark-blue/80 text-center">
        "The immediate, enthusiastic response from fans remains the brand's heartbeat today, driving a commitment to making high-quality and playful desserts accessible to everyone."
      </blockquote>
    </div>

    <!-- Our Events angle -->
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why We Do Events</h2>
      <p class="text-pauls-dark-blue/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        We're a Paul's Homemade franchisee with a singular focus: bringing the magic of Paul's to your celebrations. Whether it's a wedding, a birthday, a corporate function, or a brand activation — we show up with the scoops, the setup, and the service to make your event unforgettable.
      </p>
      <p class="text-pauls-dark-blue/70 leading-relaxed">
        Based in Johannesburg, we cater events across Gauteng and beyond. Every event is personal to us — because nothing brings people together quite like ice cream.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/events" class="text-pauls-blue font-bold hover:underline">See our setups &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- About the events team -->
    <!-- ZEE: review copy -->
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">About the Events Team</h2>
      <p class="text-pauls-dark-blue/70 leading-relaxed">
        We're the Johannesburg-based Paul's Homemade franchise events team. From weddings to corporate functions to private celebrations, we bring the full Paul's experience to your venue — the setups, the scoops, and a team that loves what they do.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-pauls-light-blue/40 py-12 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Let's make your next event special</h2>
    <p class="text-pauls-dark-blue/60 mb-6">We'd love to be part of your celebration.</p>
    <a href="/book" class="bg-pauls-blue text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
      Book Your Event
    </a>
  </section>
</Base>
